lead_paragraph: China's bid for shooting gold came up short on the opening day of the Rio Olympics and was not looking good on Sunday's day two after a two-time defending gold medalist failed to qualify.

headline.print_headline: Zhang Gives China Another Women's Air Pistol Gold
